  Sashnov Alexander's homepage
  
This is a source of my homepage. It also need symlink for directory
'files' and 'img' to dir contains files and images for page.


  Building
  
For build it you must have installed folowwing programs:

make		GNU make utilite
bash		Shell (or any other shell like sh)
m4		GNU macroprocessor
awk		GNU awk interpreter (gawk)
ImageMagick	Image processing tool


Build all project:

  make clean
  make

Archive it (buck up or distrib):

  make dist

Check local links:

  make check

Update page in internet through FTP:

  make update



Some comments


* recode to 1251 needs for hosting on newmail.ru - it puts information about document encode in
http header:

HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sat, 17 Jan 2004 07:22:36 GMT
Server: Apache/1.3.27 (Unix)
Last-Modified: Sat, 03 Jan 2004 06:47:38 GMT
ETag: "3cc9f0-1aee-3ff6658a"
Accept-Ranges: bytes
Content-Length: 6894
Content-Type: text/html; charset=windows-1251
X-Cache: MISS from ns.plesk.ru
Connection: keep-alive

Becouse I add recode to exceed validator.w3c.org warning.


* You cat configure ftp (standart ftp client) for automaticaly update your files.
For do this, create .netrc file in your home dir with contents:

ine ftp.newmail.ru
login sashnov.nm.ru
password d2k_75fh3_1x
macdef init
lcd /home/asashnov/projects/homepage
put about.html
put ayengine.html
......put other files.........
exit


